extends layout 

block content 
  div.container 
    h1.h1 Create New Message 

    if errors 
      ul.error-list 
        for error in errors 
          li.error-item!= error.msg 


    form.form.b-radius-1(method="POST")
      div.form-group
        label.form-label(for="title") Title
        input#title.form-control(type="text", name="title", value=(undefined===message ? "" : message.title))
      div.form-group
        label.form-label(for="text") Text
        textarea#text.form-textarea(type="text", name="text", value=(undefined===message ? "" : message.text))
      div.form-group
        button.nav-link.form-button(type="submit") Create Message